Navigate to List Control. In OOB form you wont have Omit new condition/Omit edit condition.So manually add the fields.
Then provide the condition in the respective fields.  

To hide new button for itil user:-

In the Omit new condition script type field , add the following script :- 


var answer;
if(gs.hasRole('itil'))
	answer = true;
else
	answer = false;
